  "abstract": "<p>Validated and accurate prognostic testing is critical for precision medicine in uveal melanoma (UM). Our aims were to (1) prospectively validate an integrated prognostic classifier combining a 15-gene expression profile (15-GEP) and PRAME RNA expression, and (2) identify clinical variables that enhance the prognostic accuracy of the 15-GEP/PRAME classifier.</p>",
